snippet.title: Salvo Subs Alpha Trailer (Spring 2024)
snippet.description:
The first trailer for Salvo Subs!

Salvo Subs is a solo development project, to be released Early Access on Steam near the end of 2024. 

Music by xyce (@xycechipmusic)

Find out more at SalvoSubs.com
